 improvement in terms of\nthe EE performance is also investigated for dense SCNs using practical energy\nmodels developed in the Green-Touch project.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Sep 2016 07:31:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Dec 2016 03:25:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 3 Jan 2017 06:36:45 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2017 22:29:51 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 26 Sep 2017 06:38:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-27"}
