ary computation. We anticipate that defining such a 'simplest task to\nfail' is a valuable benchmark for promoting future development in the field of\nartificial intelligence, evolutionary robotics and artificial life.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 25 Sep 2016 10:00:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-27"}
